This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving the attention mechanism in Neural Machine Translation models. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel mechanism to address the attention deficiency issue, which is a common problem in NMT models. 

The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). 

Finally, the paper may also belong to the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it involves the use of attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks such as image captioning.
